{"lemma":"حَرَكاتٌ","slug":"حَرَكاتٌ","root":"ح.ر.ك","root_slug":"ح-ر-ك","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ر-ك","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":8},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n7741","n7743"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%83%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"movement, motion"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"instance noun of حَرُكَ (ḥaruka): an instance of movement"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"commotion"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"physical exercise"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"stirring, impulse"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"vowel, especially of languages written in the Arabic script"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"diacritic, accent mark, especially of languages written in the Arabic script","tags":["proscribed"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"mora; a unit of time indicating how long a sound is pronounced"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ħa.ra.ka/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7741","headword_ar":"حرّكهُ","root":"Hrk","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", [inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taHoriykN","text_ar":"تَحْرِيكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He moved; put in motion; put in a state of motion, commotion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"agitation; moved about; agitated, stirred,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shook; it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K.) [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hr~k","text_ar":"حرّك"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHo$aAy^iY","text_ar":"اَحْشَايِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It agitated my bowels"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is like the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hr~k min~iY","text_ar":"حرّك مِنِّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it agitated me"},{"kind":"text","text":"], said by one who has been agitated by reason of an event or affair. (Ham p. 183.) ―         -b2-  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a letter)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"movent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made it to be immediately followed by a vowel; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sak~anahu","text_ar":"سَكَّنَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He urged him"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to go, but he went not."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, Z.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n7743","headword_ar":"حَرَكَةٌ","root":"Hrk","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Motion; commotion; agitation; contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sukuwnN","text_ar":"سُكُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Msb, K; *) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaraAkN","text_ar":"حَرَاكٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) as in the phrase,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA bihi HaraAkN","text_ar":"مَا بِهِ حَرَاكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is not in him any motion"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, K:) and, accord. to El-Khafájee,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiraAkN","text_ar":"حِرَاكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also; but this is disallowed by MF. (TA.) [The first, accord. to the Msb, is an inf. n. of un.: but see 1.] ―         -b2-  [Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Activity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"often used in this sense in the classical language, and in the present day. ―         -b3-  And A letter's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having a vowel immediately following:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a vowel"},{"kind":"text","text":"itself.]"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K"]}]}}